text: Mädchen Amick (born December 12, 1970) is an American actress. She began acting in television programs. She starred as Shelly Johnson on the television series Twin Peaks and its 1992 prequel movie Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me. She was born east of Reno, Nevada and raised in Sparks, Nevada.
